{
 "name": "RPlog_From_Diplomat_to_Spychief",
 "title": "From Diplomat to Spychief",
 "summary": "Summoned to the Bureau liaison office above O'Paal, the scarred Morganna Tazecks faces Tsaran Joir after psychological evaluations have flagged her as dangerous, violent, and emotionally volatile -- plainly unfit for diplomacy. Joir coldly strips her of all diplomatic duties, and Morganna braces for ruin, certain her career is over. Instead he hands her a CIO transfer file: she is named provisional Chief Intelligence Officer, her ruthlessness reframed as an asset for rooting out chaos. Stunned, then fiercely gratified, Morganna pledges herself to the Empire and the Emperor, and Joir directs her to her predecessor, Vice Director Pantek, to be brought up to speed. The scene marks Morganna's transformation from failed diplomat to spychief, with Joir deliberately injecting an unpredictable element into the Bureau.",
